<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-10-1264 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper abstracted discusses questions of nuclear safeguards from thepoint of view of a nuclear power plant operator. Based on fundamentaltechnological and economic problems a comprehensive survey is given ofthe IAEA and Euratom monitoring systems. The survey is followed by adiscussion of legal aspects with regard to the limits and principlesof nuclear safeguards. The final section points out legal safeguardsand briefly discusses questions of liability.</TEXT></DOC>